    5.1 Early Delivery or Late Delivery will entitle the Buyer to cancel the Order.
    5.2 Unless written notice is given by the Buyer to the contrary, the Seller must deliver the quantity
    specified on the order in one delivery. Failure by the Seller to deliver in one delivery will give
    the Buyer the option to cancel the balance of the Order with no further liability whatsoever.
